RedHatBase : Common, GnomeVFS, GnomeCUPS, StartupNotification, RedHatOnly, ODKFixes
RHFedora : RedHatBase, RHFedoraOnly
RHTaroon : RedHatBase, RHTaroonOnly
RHShrike : RedHatBase, RHShrikeOnly

